title: Deepmind’s AI Is Learning About the Art of Coding
description: AlphaDev has made small but significant improvements to decades-old C++ algorithms. Its builders say that’s just the start.

title: What Weight Watchers Offers That Ozempic Can't
description: We talk with Sima Sistani, the CEO of Weight Watchers, about applying her previous careers in social media to the company's efforts to build a digital community.
